data.title: 2018/2019 Champions League
data.text:
Champions League 2018/19. Group Stages.

Attendance: 46,067.

13. Neto (GK), 3. Rúben Vezo (11. Denis Cheryshev 57 min), 4. Jeison Murillo, 5. Gabriel, 7. Gonçalo Guedes (22. Santi Mina 70 min),

19. Leonardo Bonucci, 20. João Cancelo, 33. Federico Bernardeschi.
